blizzard (0.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * increased size of pool http objects
  * updated logic for idle thread: delay could be zero
  * increased MAX_HEADER_ITEMS and READ_HEADERS_SZ
  * treat OPTIONS request method the same way as GET
  * use log_die instead of die from coda
  * log error in case of full queue
  * improved support of MacOSX
  * added English ReadMe with Markdown format

 -- Konstantin Akimov <knstqq@gmail.com>  Wed, 10 Nov 2021 01:41:28 +0700

